{
  "page": "Warden of the South",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center;\">Warden of the South</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_South.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Warden of the South, by David Griffith © Fantasy Flight Games\"><img alt=\"Warden of the South, by David Griffith © Fantasy Flight Games\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/01/David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_South.png/350px-David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_South.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"237\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/01/David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_South.png/525px-David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_South.png 1.5x, /images/0/01/David_Griffith_Warden_of_the_South.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"font-size: 100%; margin-bottom:10px;\">Warden of the South, by David Griffith © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Office</th><td>\nSupreme general in southern <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Current Holder</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">First Holder</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Harlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Harlan Tyrell\">Harlan Tyrell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Creator</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Created</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Warden of the South</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Warden\" title=\"Warden\">warden</a> title traditionally held by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a>, the Lords of <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a> and rulers of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, on behalf of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>. The warden has been responsible for the defense of the southern lands of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> since <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Responsibilities\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Responsibilities</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Known_Wardens_of_the_South\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Wardens of the South</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Responsibilities\">Responsibilities</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_South&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Responsibilities\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Warden of the South is tasked with defending the southern regions of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> from invaders.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> When the title was created during <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>, for instance, the southern realm of <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> had not yet submitted to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_South&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Wardens_of_the_South_Adam_Lane.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Wardens_of_the_South_Adam_Lane.jpg/400px-Wardens_of_the_South_Adam_Lane.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"146\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Wardens_of_the_South_Adam_Lane.jpg/600px-Wardens_of_the_South_Adam_Lane.jpg 1.5x, /images/e/e6/Wardens_of_the_South_Adam_Lane.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Wardens_of_the_South_Adam_Lane.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Warden of the South, by Adam Lane © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Mern_IX_Gardener\" title=\"Mern IX Gardener\">Mern IX Gardener</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a>, and his kin from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a> were killed at the <a href=\"/index.php/Field_of_Fire\" title=\"Field of Fire\">Field of Fire</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>. When King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a> arrived at <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>, the castle was surrendered to him by its steward, <a href=\"/index.php/Harlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Harlan Tyrell\">Harlan Tyrell</a>. Aegon the Conqueror rewarded Harlan by naming him Warden of the South and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Paramount_of_the_Mander\" title=\"Lord Paramount of the Mander\">Lord Paramount of the Mander</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>, Aegon sent Harlan to march against <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Uller\" title=\"Uthor Uller\">Uthor Uller</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Hellholt\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord of the Hellholt\">Lord of the Hellholt</a>. Harlan's host was greatly weakened in the Dornish deserts, however, and they found the <a href=\"/index.php/Hellholt\" title=\"Hellholt\">Hellholt</a> abandoned by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a>. Harlan marched east toward <a href=\"/index.php/Vaith\" title=\"Vaith\">Vaith</a> after the <a href=\"/index.php/Defenestration_of_Sunspear\" title=\"Defenestration of Sunspear\">Defenestration of Sunspear</a>, but his host disappeared in the red sands of central Dorne in <a href=\"/index.php/5_AC\" title=\"5 AC\">5&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> When Aegon wanted to respond to Dornish attacks on <a href=\"/index.php/Nightsong\" title=\"Nightsong\">Nightsong</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/10_AC\" title=\"10 AC\">10&#160;AC</a>, young Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Theo_Tyrell\" title=\"Theo Tyrell\">Theo Tyrell</a> was reluctant to support another invasion of Dorne.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Tyrell_(lord)\" title=\"Lyonel Tyrell (lord)\">Lyonel Tyrell</a> participated in the <a href=\"/index.php/Conquest_of_Dorne\" title=\"Conquest of Dorne\">conquest of Dorne</a> by King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron I Targaryen\">Daeron I Targaryen</a>, but he was assassinated at <a href=\"/index.php/Sandstone\" title=\"Sandstone\">Sandstone</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Wardens_of_the_South\">Known Wardens of the South</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_South&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Wardens of the South\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mace_TyrellLukasz_Jaskolski.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a5/Mace_TyrellLukasz_Jaskolski.png/350px-Mace_TyrellLukasz_Jaskolski.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"224\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/a/a5/Mace_TyrellLukasz_Jaskolski.png 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mace_TyrellLukasz_Jaskolski.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a>, by Lukasz Jaskolski © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Harlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Harlan Tyrell\">Harlan Tyrell</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Theo_Tyrell\" title=\"Theo Tyrell\">Theo Tyrell</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Bertrand_Tyrell\" title=\"Bertrand Tyrell\">Bertrand Tyrell</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Matthos_Tyrell\" title=\"Matthos Tyrell\">Matthos Tyrell</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Tyrell_(Lord)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lyonel Tyrell (Lord)\">Lyonel Tyrell</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(Longthorn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (Longthorn)\">Leo Tyrell</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Luthor_Tyrell\" title=\"Luthor Tyrell\">Luthor Tyrell</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_South&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Harlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Harlan Tyrell\">Tyrell</a> yielded up the keys to the castle without a fight and pledged his support to the conquering king. In reward <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a> granted him <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a> and all its domains, naming him Warden of the South and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Paramount_of_the_Mander\" title=\"Lord Paramount of the Mander\">Lord Paramount of the Mander</a>, and giving him dominion over all <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a>'s former vassals.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Warden_of_the_South&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aegon's Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/Social_Structure_Moat_Cailin_and_More\">Social Structure, Moat Cailin, and More</a>, June 10, 2002</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Reign of the Dragon - The Wars of King Aegon I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_o